text: Hermenegildo Candeias (born 17 April 1934) is a Portuguese gymnast. He competed in six events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Portuguese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Portugal Category:Gymnasts at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Oeiras, Portugal
